(43, 1, '2015-02-03 14:38:50', '2015-02-03 14:38:50', '<pre>Stayble is developing a minimally invasive injection-based treatment against chronic low back pain. Stayble offer a solution that actually will remove the pain for the patients without the need for surgery.</pre>\r\n[ezcol_1half]\r\n<h2>The Problem</h2>\r\n[/ezcol_1half]\r\n\r\n[ezcol_end_both]\r\n\r\nStayble focuses on patients suffering from cLBP where the pain is caused by a leakage of inflammatory substances from the disc centre. The leakage occurs through tears in the disc wall caused by an aging process of the disc.\r\n\r\n[ezcol_end_both]\r\n\r\n[ezcol_1half]\r\n\r\n<a href="http://localhost/phptest/stayble-old/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/disk-med-pilar.png"><img class="alignnone wp-image-357 " src="http://localhost/phptest/stayble-old/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/disk-med-pilar.png" alt="" width="317" height="187" /></a>\r\n\r\n[/ezcol_1half]\r\n\r\n[ezcol_1half]\r\n<h6>DIRECT COSTS\r\nOF €22 000</h6>\r\n[/ezcol_1half]\r\n\r\n[ezcol_end_left]\r\n\r\n[ezcol_1half]\r\n\r\nToday spinal fusion is the only treatment for patients with cLBP who do not respond to the usual conservative treatment of analgesics and physiotherapy.\r\n\r\nThe direct cost of a spinal fusion is € 22 000 and is followed by up to 6 months of rehabilitation with accompanying work absence of up to two years. In addition only 60% of the treated patients will actually become better from the treatment while 40 % remain unchanged or become worse\r\n\r\n[/ezcol_1half]\r\n\r\n[ezcol_1half]\r\n\r\n<img class=" wp-image-320 size-full alignnone" src="http://localhost/phptest/stayble-old/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/bubblan-24-bitars.png" alt="" width="231" height="245" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[/ezcol_1half]\r\n\r\n[ezcol_1half]\r\n<h2>STAYBLES UNIQUE TREATMENT</h2>\r\n[/ezcol_1half]\r\n\r\n[ezcol_end_both]\r\n\r\n[ezcol_1third]\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone wp-image-328 size-full" src="http://localhost/phptest/stayble-old/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/disk-stelnad-o-inte-stelnad.png" alt="" width="233" height="285" />\r\n\r\n[/ezcol_1third]\r\n\r\n[ezcol_2third]\r\n\r\nStayble is developing an injection-based treatment against discogenic pain that will effectively remove the pain and the need for spinal fusion. Stayble’s treatment offers the patient a completely new way to treat its chronic low back pain and will drastically change the way surgeons treat cLBP.\r\n\r\nThe injection treatment works in the way of transforming the disc centre from being a liquid into solid state. The transformation of the disc will remove the pain-causing component (the leakage) and in a simple, cost-saving and minimally-invasive way eliminate the pain for the patients.\r\n\r\nThe treatment is assumed to be effective within 4 weeks, last the patient’s entire life and require no need for rehabilitation\r\n\r\n[/ezcol_2third]\r\n\r\n[ezcol_end_both]\r\n<h2>STAYBLE’S TREATMENT IN SHORT</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Minimally-invasive single injection</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Targeting the pain provoking mechanism</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Performed in an open ward</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Estimated to have low COGS</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nDo you want to know more?\r\nread our <strong> one-pager</strong>', 'Technology', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'technology', '', '', '2015-02-19 15:51:00', '2015-02-19 15:51:00', '', 0, 'http://localhost/phptest/stayble/?page_id=43', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(44, 1, '2015-02-03 14:38:50', '2015-02-03 14:38:50', 'Here it''s going to be a text about the technology that Stayble uses.', 'Technology', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '43-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-02-03 14:38:50', '2015-02-03 14:38:50', '', 43, 'http://localhost/phptest/stayble/43-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(45, 1, '2015-02-03 14:39:46', '2015-02-03 14:39:46', '<pre>Stayble therapeutics is developing a minimally invasive injection-based treatment against chronic low back pain triggered by tears in the disc caused by disc degeneration. Stayble offer a solution that actually will remove the pain for the patients without the need for surgery.</pre>\r\n[ezcol_1half]\r\n<h2>Market info</h2>\r\n[/ezcol_1half]\r\n\r\n[ezcol_end_both]\r\n\r\n[ezcol_2third]\r\n\r\nStayble’s initial market will be patients that today receive a spinal fusion for their discogenic pain. This patient group consist of approximately 100 000 fusions performed yearly in the US and EU. A group of patients that Stayble will be able to charge a high price and verify its treatment procedure.\r\n\r\nIn a second phase the aim is to target the market of patients suffering from moderate discogenic pain for whom the risks and the costs associated with a spinal fusion exceeds the likely benefit. This will be a much larger patient group but where we will be harder to get initial acceptance and where the pricing will be lower.\r\n\r\n[/ezcol_2third]\r\n\r\n[ezcol_1third]\r\n\r\n<a href="http://localhost/phptest/stayble-old/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/bubblan_02.png"><img class="alignnone wp-image-316 size-full" src="http://localhost/phptest/stayble-old/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/bubblan_02.png" alt="" width="231" height="245" /></a>\r\n\r\n[/ezcol_1third]\r\n\r\n[ezcol_end_both]\r\n\r\n[ezcol_1half]\r\n<h2>Market penetration and estimated peak sale</h2>\r\n[/ezcol_1half]\r\n\r\n[ezcol_end_both]\r\n\r\n[ezcol_1half]\r\n\r\nThe market penetration is estimated to start rather slow to gain acceptance of the new treatment procedure on the market. This due to that spinal surgeons are a relatively conservative group. It is, however, very well connected with a large community with will mean that once Stayble’s treatment will be accepted on the market by the main drivers we estimate a more rapid adoption.\r\n\r\nThis segment involves in the initial market focus approximately 32 000 patients (US, EU). At a sales price of €4000 this equals to a yearly income of 128MEUR just in the segment of fusions (towards degenerative disc disease) today. When the product has been accepted on the market we estimate an extensive increase in usage towards a broader indication\r\n\r\n[/ezcol_1half]\r\n\r\n[ezcol_1half]\r\n<h6>Estimated product price of €4000</h6>\r\n<h6>128 MEUR in peak sales</h6>\r\n<h6>Great possibility to expand the market</h6>\r\n[/ezcol_1half]', 'Market', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'market', '', '', '2015-02-18 19:39:49', '2015-02-18 19:39:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost/phptest/stayble/?page_id=45', 0, 'page', '', 0),
