(265, 1, '2015-02-18 05:44:58', '2015-02-18 05:44:58', '<p class="ingress">Stayble Therapeutics has patented the use of an existing drug substance, which is assumed to permanently relieve the patient from back pain within a timeframe of 4 weeks. The substance is well documented and has been used for decades in humans allowing a relatively fast, inexpensive and low-risk route to market.</p>\r\n\r\nThe project is currently in pre-clinical development with the goal of entering clinical trials in 2016. Stayble Therapeutics aims to secure further funding of €500 000 during 2015 in order to finance the development of the project until first concept studies in humans.\r\n\r\nBehind Stayble Therapeutics stands an experienced, multidisciplinary team including a world-renowned back-pain researcher, experienced bio-entrepreneurs and former big pharma senior management. Our vision is that this treatment concept will reach out to millions of patients who are disabled by chronic back pain. We believe this drug has the potential to drastically reduce the suffering from a widespread, incapacitating condition.', 'About us', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '47-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-02-18 05:44:58', '2015-02-18 05:44:58', '', 47, 'http://localhost/phptest/stayble-old/47-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
